陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6aeb6cc1509c9351e1dac527771c2de48cbc2c4a","tid":1544733,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T11:31:40.000Z","msg":"[物理學] 見到多警察戴彩色鏡片，諗住防laser，有片有教學<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535501</a>"},{"pid":"704d801133e66ad7f1b4f67fd1f8b6aea585394e","tid":1544733,"uid":116480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T11:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e874bb29e2f576fddec96bd10530b97fa9f23c","tid":1544733,"uid":133534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"704d801133e66ad7f1b4f67fd1f8b6aea585394e","tid":1544733,"uid":116480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T11:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T11:51:56.000Z","msg":"Share"},{"pid":"d860d66794748bffd9cb825272184e2052a227e6","tid":1544733,"uid":273059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T